---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Bomfather Solutions - Secure Software Supply Chain"
  description="Discover how Bomfather's kernel-level dependency tracking can enhance your software supply chain security and compliance."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-light-blue">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading mb-4">Software Supply Chain Solutions</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-mid-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Bomfather provides comprehensive solutions for software supply chain security, compliance, and integrity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Enterprise Supply Chain Security</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            For enterprise organizations with complex software supply chains, Bomfather provides unparalleled visibility and verification.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Complete dependency tracking at the kernel level</li>
            <li>Integration with existing CI/CD pipelines</li>
            <li>Compliance reporting for regulatory requirements</li>
            <li>Tamper-evident verification of build integrity</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-lg">
            Secure your software supply chain with accurate, comprehensive dependency information that goes beyond traditional
            manifest-based approaches.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-light-gray p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Use Case: Financial Services</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Financial institutions using Bomfather gain complete visibility into their software dependencies, 
            helping them meet stringent security and compliance requirements.
          </p>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-4 py-2 italic">
            "Bomfather provides the missing piece in our software supply chain security strategy by capturing 
            dependencies that traditional tools miss."
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-light-gray">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Key Solution Benefits</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Enhanced Security</h3>
          <p>
            Identify and mitigate security vulnerabilities by having a complete picture of all dependencies used in your software.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Compliance Readiness</h3>
          <p>
            Meet regulatory requirements with cryptographically verifiable documentation of your software components.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Build Integrity</h3>
          <p>
            Ensure your software hasn't been tampered with using verifiable dependency tracking and cryptographic proofs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Secure Your Software Supply Chain?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Start using Bomfather today to gain kernel-level truth about your software dependencies.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary-dark transition duration-300">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/bitbomdev/bomfather" class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300">
          View on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout> 